{"tid":1361734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(置頂) 建議大家睇post唔好只係睇正負評","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:57:43.000Z","uid":24927,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84f8bfab453313df6b655833815a6ab9e36ec9d2","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"頭先有人post黃毓民屌鳩朱凱迪條片 勁撚多負評 <br />\n咁我一定聽左佢屌咩先 發現黃毓民講既野係好啱 <br />\n跟住樓下班人第一句就話人分化撚 <br />\n可能朱凱迪經驗唔夠 可以教下佢先唔洗一黎就屌<br />\n但其實連登真係好撚多人睇正負評黎屌就算 唔係第一日咁<br />\n 我好撚懷疑屌個班人係完全冇睇過條片 冇錯 佢一定係私怨撚黎 但係不如你睇哂條片先講野<br />\n唔好第一句就黎屌人分化撚ok? <br />\n成班傻鳩見人屌又一齊屌<br />\n咁既風氣真係要改下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231c4f141f1f598d82a2949658ec19634ebf71c6","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"90a4d284b0d57f111c78174e6966a659ea0232e1","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"71f32ce9162eb58be790e6721c19a4a84555c550","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"9cc41c011090053ee363494a6e6fb0d07f4979d2","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"呢樣野好重要 希望有人幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4988f9e6a9d4f4c693fc8df9b2c782df66a001a5","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:23:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"59797ca7aeb9822c934c9d7e3d6d5b80ac96d54d","tid":1361734,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=540&amp;v=_DiJNOyXPK4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D540%26v%3D_DiJN